{"word":"H7194 - קָשַׁר - qâshar - kaw-shar' - Bind","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קָשַׁר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>qâshar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kaw-shar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Bind"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கட்டிக்கொள், கட்டு, கட்டுப்பாடு பண்ணு, பூணு. பூட்டு, கட்டிவை, இணைக்கப்படு, இசைந்திரு, இணை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to bind, to tie, to bind together, to league together, to conspire"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to bind, to confine"},{"paragraph":"2) to league together, to conspire"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal) to be bound, to be bound up"},{"paragraph":"c) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to bind on"},{"paragraph":"2) to bind fast"},{"paragraph":"3) to bind, to tie"},{"paragraph":"4) to bind to oneself"},{"paragraph":"d) (Pual) robust, vigorous (participle)"},{"paragraph":"e) (Hithpael) to conspire"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>tie</i>, physically (<i>gird</i>, <i>confine</i>, <i>compact</i>) or mentally (in <i>love</i>, <i>league</i>): - bind (up), (make a) conspire (-acy, -ator), join together, knit, stronger, work [treason]."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7194 - קָשַׁר - qâshar - kaw-shar'/7194\">H7194</a>, <a href=\"#/H7195 - קֶשֶׁר - qesher - keh'-sher/7195\">H7195</a>, <a href=\"#/H7196 - קִשֻּׁר - qishshur - kish-shoor'/7196\">H7196</a>"}]}